[I] A 3DS emulator project based on Citra

[T] Azahar is an open-source 3DS emulator project based on Citra. It was
[T] created from the merging of PabloMK7's Citra fork and the Lime3DS project,
[T] both of which emerged shortly after Citra was taken down.

